Column metadata for Table and Views ( table and view column metadata change is done in IMPALA)

TABLE

ALTER TABLE db.table_name
ALTER COLUMN ID SET COMMENT "Allegation ID";
ALTER TABLE db.table_name
ALTER COLUMN name SET COMMENT "name of the person";
ALTER TABLE db.table_name
ALTER COLUMN address SET COMMENT "address of the person";


VIEW (repeating alter view is not needed here)

